OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778083869
OL,3,CNearly 25,000 oysters returned to
OL,4,CCornish river to enhance future stock
OL,6,FNearly 25,000 live native oysters have
OL,7,Fbeen returned to the sea in the River
OL,8,FFal in Cornwall to try to enhance the
OL,9,Fstock for the future and improve the
OL,10,Fmarine habitat.
OL,12,FThis is the second year a team from
OL,13,FCornwall Inshore Fisheries and
OL,14,FConservation Authority, who manage the
OL,15,Funique fishery, have taken on this
OL,16,Fproject.
OL,18,FThe team buy direct from the oyster
OL,19,Ffishers, count and weigh the oysters,
OL,20,Fthis year 1.8 tonnes, then distribute
OL,21,Fthem back on the sea bed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
