FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778083869
OL,3,CNearly 25,000 oysters returned to
OL,4,CCornish river to enhance future stock
OL,6,FColin Trundle, the principal
OL,7,Fscientific officer for Cornwall IFCA,
OL,8,Fsays they're trying to ensure the
OL,9,Foyster population here is thriving.
OL,11,FColin said: "What we're trying to do
OL,12,Fis increase the density slightly in
OL,13,Fcertain areas to improve the larval
OL,14,Fproduction and therefore they'll turn
OL,15,Finto spat, and then we're likely to
OL,16,Fhave a much more productive fishery.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778083869
OL,3,CNearly 25,000 oysters returned to
OL,4,CCornish river to enhance future stock
OL,6,F"This is the last wild capture native
OL,7,Foyster fishery in England now, it's
OL,8,Fthe last fishery in Europe that's
OL,9,Fexploited by oar and sail only. So
OL,10,Fit's very, very low impact, we're
OL,11,Flooking at maintaining the future of
OL,12,Fthe fishery and trying to make it
OL,13,Fbetter over time".
OL,15,FA total of 18 oyster fishers from the
OL,16,FRiver Fal joined the project including
OL,17,Ffather and son, Zane and Louis Dutton
OL,18,FThompson.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778083869
OL,3,CNearly 25,000 oysters returned to
OL,4,CCornish river to enhance future stock
OL,6,FZane said: "There are other
OL,7,Fregeneration projects around the
OL,8,Fcountry which we've sold to but it
OL,9,Fseems a bit silly really, because
OL,10,Fthat's our stock that we're sending
OL,11,Foff elsewhere and this just all came
OL,12,Ftogether with the increase in the ring
OL,13,Fsize, I think it's very positive.
OL,14,FPlus, they put you in where they know,
OL,15,Fwhere they know the fishery needs them
OL,16,Fas well".
OL,18,FChris Vinnicombe's family have been
OL,19,Fdredging for oysters on the River Fal
OL,20,Ffor generations.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778083869
OL,3,CNearly 25,000 oysters returned to
OL,4,CCornish river to enhance future stock
OL,6,FHe says he wants the traditional
OL,7,Ffishery to carry on for future
OL,8,Fgenerations: "It makes more sense to
OL,9,Fdo this rather than sell them away to
OL,10,Fenhance other areas. So this is a sort
OL,11,Fof win win, a win for the fishery and
OL,12,Fa win for the fishermen."
OL,14,FA group of marine biology students
OL,15,Ffrom the University of Exeter helped
OL,16,Fto re-lay some of the oysters.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778083869
OL,3,CNearly 25,000 oysters returned to
OL,4,CCornish river to enhance future stock
OL,6,FStudent Bel Mansell, whose
OL,7,Fdissertation was about oysters, said:
OL,8,F"They're really important for the
OL,9,Fbenthic habitat and they support other
OL,10,Fspecies as well.
OL,12,F"So redistributing them makes the
OL,13,Fwhole space more healthy, it makes the
OL,14,Fsea bed more healthy and it's really
OL,15,Fimportant to get involved."
OL,17,FThe project's partly funded by
OL,18,Freinvesting the licence fee oyster
OL,19,Ffishers pay IFCA for each dredge they
OL,20,Fuse.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778083869
OL,3,CNearly 25,000 oysters returned to
OL,4,CCornish river to enhance future stock
OL,6,FColin added "what we're doing is we're
OL,7,Flooking at maintaining coastal
OL,8,Fcommunities in terms of being able to
OL,9,Fmake them economically viable and
OL,10,Fgoing into the future.
OL,12,F"So yeah, public money is going into
OL,13,Fit, but we put it to good use because
OL,14,Fit's going back to the people that are
OL,15,Fputting it towards us."
OL,17,FCornwall IFCA hope this project will
OL,18,Fhelp improve oyster stocks in the
OL,19,FRiver Fal, boost the marine habitat
OL,20,Fand help secure the future of this
OL,21,Fhistoric Cornish fishery.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
